casebody.data:
ROUSE
v.
FORSYTH COUNTY DSS 1PA19-1 Supreme Court of North Carolina. May 31, 2019 Gloria L. Woods, Assistant County Attorney, for Forsyth County Department of Social Services. Benjamin P. Winikoff, Attorney at Law, for Rouse, Teressa B.

Gloria L. Woods, Assistant County Attorney.

Amended

The following order has been entered on the Motion for Extension of Time to File Brief filed on the 30th of May 2019 by Petitioner:

"Motion Allowed by order of the Court in conference, this the 31st of May 2019."

Petitioner shall have up to and including the 10th day of July 2019 to file and serve his/her brief with this Court.
